{"tid":1462592,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"HKBN 間接為 TVB 帶來1.82億收入，8月18日必須回應！","createTime":"2019-08-13T10:55:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-21T15:07:47.000Z","uid":267969,"like":48,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":39,"replies":[{"pid":"46550c231ce2bc2ca32d0ee39ec19f6e69f680d0","tid":1462592,"uid":267969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T10:55:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />為咗無顧慮咁打擊紅媒，所以6月申請咗呢個P牌acc<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />舊HKBN post正評多，但真係去攻HKBN嘅留言少<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />P牌仔用咗今日嘅quota，希望大家幫推下<strong>行動post</strong><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />以後只出行動post，唔會出9up post，希望大家可憐下抵制團隊，追蹤我個acc同幫推<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />FB又開始打壓我哋<br />\n<br />\n＊＊＊<br />\n資料顯示，myTV SUPER 為TVB<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">全年賺1.82億</span>，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">係1.82億呀！</span></span></strong><br />\n香港寬頻 HKBN 作為最大伙伴，以綑綁式銷售方法為TVB 續命，實在罪無可恕！<br />\n<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EdW4qUT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEdW4qUT.jpg&h=7e9c0132&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n本台收到眾多投訴，HKBN夾硬送myTV SUPER嗰舊廢鐵俾用戶，正所謂羊毛出自羊身上，呢啲綑綁式服務完全不能接受<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>HKBN用戶表示：根本cut唔撚到myTV SUPER嘅！</strong></span><br />\n<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Qo5o4d4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQo5o4d4.png&h=951215c1&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">各位手足，我哋唔係唔開佢拖呀？</span></strong></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/HongKongBroadbandNetwork/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FHongKongBroadbandNetwork%2F&d=HBLsGxwPt4tNlCAdiZVEvu6cow1LS9WQT%2BeJ8I%2F17x8%3D&h=afcee60b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/HongKongBroadbandNetwork/</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong>有埋留言Template，唔好同我講你連copy and paste 都懶：<br />\n</strong><span style=\"color: red;\">記得四揀一呀</span>，歡迎自由發揮<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我用香港寬頻上網係為咗接收全面資訊，而唔係俾錢你用嚟支持無綫電視假新聞，請8月18日前回應！<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />拒絕綑綁myTV SUPER，否則香港人綑綁式解約，轉Netvigator轉有線，請8月18日前回應！<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我咁辛苦先到cut有線，唔好迫我返去得唔得？請8月18日前回應！<br />\n<br />\n<em>非HKBN用戶：</em><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />你唔結束myTV SUPER綑綁式服務，我就一世唔會用HKBN，請8月18日前回應！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">如果HKBN 一星期內唔回應訴求，合約完一於轉會啦<br />\n唔好忍喇～</span></strong></span><br />\n<strong>推介：</strong><br />\nNetvigator - 送NowTV 機頂盒<br />\n有線寬頻 - 送有線電視（好似係）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PrdaKfp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPrdaKfp.jpg&h=f7603dec&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/sayno2tvb/photos/a.419928515530670/429497331240455/?type=3&amp;theater\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fsayno2tvb%2Fphotos%2Fa.419928515530670%2F429497331240455%2F%3Ftype%3D3%26theater&d=HBLsGxwPt4tNlCAdiZVEvu6cow1LS9WQT%2BeJ8I%2F17x8%3D&h=a7a9345c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/sayno2tvb/photos/a.419928515530670/429497331240455/?type=3&amp;theater</a></span>"},{"pid":"af8298d8ac2d32bfa774bc900d125b7396ba7c8e","tid":1462592,"uid":267969,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T10:55:34.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">重要消息請留意#2回覆</span></strong></span><br />\n＊＊＊<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">大家幫手推介FB俾朋友</span><br />\n務求將抵制TVB運動<span style=\"color: red;\">推出公海</span></strong></span><br />\n<strong>抵制TVB好Easy，LIKE數就是力量，嚇怕廣告商</strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong>Facebook: </strong><a href=\"http://www.facebook.com/sayno2tvb\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fsayno2tvb&d=HBLsGxwPt4tNlCAdiZVEvu6cow1LS9WQT%2BeJ8I%2F17x8%3D&h=0dd254f3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">www.facebook.com/sayno2tvb</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong>TVB廣告客戶名單 (消費前諗清楚): </strong> <a href=\"http://bit.ly/2JSJaQK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2JSJaQK&d=HBLsGxwPt4tNlCAdiZVEvu6cow1LS9WQT%2BeJ8I%2F17x8%3D&h=7a8a3eca\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2JSJaQK</a><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">已加入myTV SUPER廣告、產品代言清單</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">TG 抵制廣告行動組: <a href=\"https://t.me/sayno2tvb\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fsayno2tvb&d=HBLsGxwPt4tNlCAdiZVEvu6cow1LS9WQT%2BeJ8I%2F17x8%3D&h=4b75f414\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/sayno2tvb</a><br />\nTG 狙擊活動行動組: <a href=\"https://t.me/tvbfucker\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Ftvbfucker&d=HBLsGxwPt4tNlCAdiZVEvu6cow1LS9WQT%2BeJ8I%2F17x8%3D&h=60af0800\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/tvbfucker</a><br />\nTG channel: <a href=\"https://t.me/shittytvb\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fshittytvb&d=HBLsGxwPt4tNlCAdiZVEvu6cow1LS9WQT%2BeJ8I%2F17x8%3D&h=4be612f0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/shittytvb</a></span>"},{"pid":"eb2126bf78e5168ddcea25a62a17ff881d09d1a6","tid":1462592,"uid":267969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T10:56:01.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">送上HKBN Marketing Team 老細電郵，<br />\n想親自同佢溝通亦得～</span></strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nEmail: samuel.hui@hkbn.com.hk, kim.hue@hkbn.com.hk <br />\n<br />\nDear Mr. HUI &amp; Mr. HUE, <br />\n<br />\n<strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><ins>Formal complaint against bundled contract of myTV SUPER</ins></div></strong><br />\nI am writing to lodge a formal complaint against HKBN regarding the bundled contract of myTV SUPER box.<br />\n<br />\nAs one of the loyal customers of your company, network service provided by HKBN is highly appreciated and is reputable among the industry. However, the bundled contract of installing myTV SUPER box is an unreasonable agreement, if not absurd, to force customers paying for undesirable installations. <br />\n<br />\nRecently, controversy on extradition bill sparked shockwaves among society and escalated to a large-scale social campaign. Instead of upholding Code of Ethics of journalists, TVB adopted the approach of distortion, news suppression and censorship. Unfairness, inaccuracy and conjecture is now the image presented by the news of TVB.<br />\n<br />\nBeing a company serving Hong Kong citizens, I believe HKBN is an enterprise which will always stand with us. Reviewing the bundled terms will not only benefit the customers but also the image of HKBN. I herewith strongly urge HKBN to WITHDRAW the bundled terms of installing myTV SUPER and I will consider advance termination of contract as one of my options if the suggestion above is not accepted.<br />\n<br />\nThank you and I am looking forward to hearing from you soon.<br />\n<br />\nYours sincerely,<br />\nA HK citizen and a HKBN customer"},{"pid":"d04fee7dcecb0c9ba2b83e76fd3911f9724324c3","tid":1462592,"uid":267969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T10:58:01.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">全新ig page登場，歡迎大力關注</span></strong></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/sayno2tvb/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fsayno2tvb%2F&d=HBLsGxwPt4tNlCAdiZVEvu6cow1LS9WQT%2BeJ8I%2F17x8%3D&h=08b5130d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/sayno2tvb/</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">巴打報料，原來 和記寬頻 都有綑綁：</span><br />\n洗埋佢老味啦！</strong></span><br />\n和記寬頻FB<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/HGCbroadband/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FHGCbroadband%2F&d=HBLsGxwPt4tNlCAdiZVEvu6cow1LS9WQT%2BeJ8I%2F17x8%3D&h=a8232614\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/HGCbroadband/</a>"},{"pid":"9caafd1f81201e4944257e0cff0430d511da65a3","tid":1462592,"uid":75759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T11:00:18.000Z","msg":"push<br />\n追究721<br />\n811"},{"pid":"4fd2d66e89fa4f83856bd51a0fb85a5561769700","tid":1462592,"uid":267969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9caafd1f81201e4944257e0cff0430d511da65a3","tid":1462592,"uid":75759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T11:00:18.000Z","msg":"push<br />\n追究721<br />\n811"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T11:01:22.000Z","msg":"我揀分類係「新聞」啱唔啱？"},{"pid":"0f94d8bcb72b8d40dc6330be87499bb10fc0385f","tid":1462592,"uid":20285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T11:02:45.000Z","msg":"612 721 811"},{"pid":"cefc10455d8522389ef87530edc739c635d8a6e2","tid":1462592,"uid":265902,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T11:12:14.000Z","msg":"P牌唔可以評分？what?"},{"pid":"6e86d3d9a299605e007224466e95eeaf88877d20","tid":1462592,"uid":267969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cefc10455d8522389ef87530edc739c635d8a6e2","tid":1462592,"uid":265902,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T11:12:14.000Z","msg":"P牌唔可以評分？what?"},"citedBy":0,"replyT